#!/bin/sh

if [ $# -eq 0 ]
  then
    echo "Usage: `basename "$0"` PID"
    exit 1
fi

# Create a live session
lttng create py_logging --live

# Enable all Python agent (logger) events
lttng track --userspace --pid $1
lttng enable-event --python --all

lttng start
